messages.message: Hey team -- a reminder that if you work on a bug reported by the field in the EPD project, please actively update its status. I am finding a good amount of tickets already being looked at (from the linked Slack thread) but the tickets still sits in backlog. I'm sure that the bug reporter would be very happy to see their ticket resolved or get any update from the eng team -- updating the ticket is the best way to let them know.
